column1: # title: Ming Dynasty Courier Routes and Postal Stations
# places: places_courier.csv

# pub_date: 2014

# description: The Late Ming Dynasty Courier Stations and Routes were compiled primarily from the "Mingdai Yizhankao" by YANG Zhengtai
column2: supplemented for some areas with information derived from the 1908 Postal Atlas. The Courier Stations and Routes were developed for use in an online network analyst application
column3: which calculates the shortest route between selected postal stations on the fly:    http://maps.cga.harvard.edu/chinapostoffice/
